5,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fc145e19a2451fccfb49e2dfdda627fb58db872","tid":711124,"uid":130040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣搞到佢得返半隻？[img]assets/faces/dog/touch.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n玩沖浪比人個頭盔撞到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487a169223dc6fb201103a5e38c4d871f540f87c","tid":711124,"uid":4689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"巴打宜家有無消息？<br />\n我同你嘅情況一樣 仲要跌到隻門牙爆左出嚟，想篐翻入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b0d7956c4fa36ae17b40ee2fa1550a6f4b154c","tid":711124,"uid":83799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:19:03.000Z","msg":"有牙套唔會箍唔到<br />\n我屋企人之前都撞崩咗個門牙  要帶牙套<br />\n之後去箍牙   個牙醫有留意到佢嘅牙套<br />\n佢有提到箍嘅時間候會注意力度方向<br />\n但都可以照箍<br />\n結果到依家箍咗成年半<br />\n差唔多完成成個療程<br />\n就黎可以拆箍<br />\n<br />\n不過佢睇嗰個係專科牙醫<br />\n同埋佢嗰隻係傳統鋼釘箍<br />\n建議樓主揾多一兩間牙醫問問"}]}